{"tid":2339571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Alicehaha]因開網店賣淘寶餐具及虐待蝦佳而被追擊嘅倒米災星蝦乾-AKA怨婦界林鄭(29)","createTime":"2020-12-24T17:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T17:39:34.000Z","uid":307961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"221d4adbb3e8d3539e18b2d4efcb8f3e15c30e09","tid":2339571,"uid":307961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:39:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>[Alice HaHa]因開網店賣淘寶餐具及虐待蝦佳而被追擊嘅倒米災星蝦乾-AKA怨婦界KOL</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"xx-large\">蝦式虐兒</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：點解嗌佢蝦佳？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WQTfuc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WQTfuc.jpg&h=59224218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：蝦乾平時睇咩育兒書？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96Apt1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96Apt1c.png&h=4757ca87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26r4t1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26r4t1f.png&h=45a97197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為一個裝備撚 佢應該買完就當睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom<span class=\"red\">藍定凌蒲銘心絲打</span><br />\n育兒書內容係有講解咩係結晶尿<br />\n有書卷味嘅文青系KOL 蝦乾表示睇完覺得好實用<br />\n但睇完都以為係自己飲過牛奶食咗蛋個仔先屙有色尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：蝦乾會唔會成日抱bb㗎？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNVkMOs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNVkMOs.png&h=95e6e10b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緊係唔會啦 又麻煩 一陣搞到佢獨立唔到咪死<br />\n我點做自己嘢行街買名牌同煮我啲乾掙掙嘅嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：蝦毛最似乜嘢卡通人物？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFsbTuu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFsbTuu.png&h=5a158ace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51ZtVHY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51ZtVHY.png&h=de278e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係Charlie Brown<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為大家都係一樣咁木口木面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：有咩方法上奶？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxQqx93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxQqx93.png&h=af66426e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑糖珍珠鮮奶<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：結晶尿成因係咩？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1E1TnpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1E1TnpP.png&h=9318eba1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ghOVKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ghOVKR.jpg&h=f8a68076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為唔夠奶水就會有結晶尿<br />\n咁點解會唔夠奶水？<br />\n鬼咩肉又唔食多嚿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WyRTyj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WyRTyj.png&h=c3e9f914&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAwPFdq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAwPFdq.png&h=ff363c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成日食埋啲冇營養嘅嘢<br />\n又話要減肥<br />\n邊有奶水出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：正常2個月嘅bb應該識咩？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dxag4Fx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxag4Fx.gif&h=fdb393a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知 識轉身<br />\n不過蝦毛仲未識轉<br />\n所以要練習下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">臭蝦乾唔好以為del咗片就可以當冇發生過 <br />\n呢度留哂底㗎喇</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：蝦乾係點同蝦毛沖涼？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcgLX1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcgLX1o.png&h=a5b4f9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZBzRmE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZBzRmE.gif&h=aa8e6e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據佢之前條片（已del）<br />\n佢哋2公婆由個bb一路喊<br />\n自己就慢手慢腳斯斯然咁拍片冇理過個仔<br />\n背景音樂配搭就係蝦毛嘅喊聲<br />\n當然就畀媽媽們圍插啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00OuFgJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00OuFgJ.png&h=5af586c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiaMHu4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiaMHu4.png&h=1b3bf4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係蝦乾解釋話係<span class=\"red\">享受緊</span>quality time<br />\n似係你享受緊多過你個仔享受<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：平時係點同蝦毛出街？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xM0MXF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xM0MXF.png&h=cd55a44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用揹帶<br />\n不過用錯咁解姐<br />\n嗰陣蝦毛先得1個月<br />\n正常係唔可以用呢種包法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：有冇請陪月？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKkdnwO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKkdnwO.png&h=9338c9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spJZh5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspJZh5b.png&h=70c4ea32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hm6zRqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhm6zRqe.png&h=fbd32156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緊係有啦<br />\n話哂陪月都係畀錢請<br />\n佢做得唔好都可以屌佢<br />\n但係四大長老就唔同<br />\n唔屌得 所以不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：點解會生小朋友？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwJKuc7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwJKuc7.png&h=07c77cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為人有我有<br />\n咁我咪生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：點解會叫佢怨婦界kol？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWyeRr6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWyeRr6.png&h=da0bafaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQtqX68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQtqX68.png&h=616b0f97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98UhPet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98UhPet.png&h=b9ecbed8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDjs4f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDjs4f0.png&h=1c15b5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTW7jPo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTW7jPo.png&h=01acbe4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未生之前怨老公都算<br />\n而家怨埋個仔<br />\n實至名歸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：蝦毛有咩玩具玩？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oS3KP0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oS3KP0.png&h=20b07809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蝦乾買channel耳環<span class=\"red\">用淨</span>嘅絲帶當玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">問：黑房論係咩？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Azi5azF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzi5azF.png&h=2ca2ec4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}